    "body": "> Thank you for the report and PR to fix the issue.\n> \n> Since there is already a related PR, do you think that [#7019](https://github.com/starship/starship/pull/7019) would also address your issue?\n\nYes, PR #7019 should address this issue when `git_metrics.mode = \"all\"`, including fallback paths (reftable/sparse/use_git_executable). I’m happy to consolidate there and add/adjust tests for this scenario. Could you confirm whether you prefer fixing this only via #7019, or keeping a separate minimal fix?\n",
